    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 因前景疲软而暴跌，表明美国需求放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/airbnb-gives-soft-outlook-on-signs-of-slowing-demand-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airbnb Inc. 连续第三个季度发布令人失望的业绩展望，并警告美国游客需求放缓，随后其股价大幅下跌 — — 这表明，即使在夏季旅游旺季，旅游支出势头也将继续减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/airbnb-gives-soft-outlook-on-signs-of-slowing-demand-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:04:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业重返债务市场，推动销售额突破 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/corporate-america-stampedes-into-debt-as-sales-pass-1-trillion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业借款人以 2020 年以来最快的速度出售投资级债券，因为企业利用较低的收益率在 11 月大选之前发行债券——即使在周一市场暴跌导致市场短暂冻结之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/corporate-america-stampedes-into-debt-as-sales-pass-1-trillion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:39:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
